        "subheading": "<p><strong>LEARN WITH US</strong></p>",
        "title": "<h3>Guide to Choosing a Vintage-Inspired Engagement Ring</h3>",
        "description": "<p>There is something undeniably romantic about a vintage-inspired engagement ring. Rich in detail and storytelling, these designs draw from the artistry of past eras while offering the durability and wearability required for modern life. Whether you're drawn to intricate craftsmanship, old-world charm or the sentiment of a future heirloom, a vintage-inspired ring can be a beautiful way to honour both history and your own love story.<br/> </p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
    "22942553-01da-4697-89ac-f500b502883f": {
      "type": "content-list",
      "blocks": {
        "template--16177341137065__22942553-01da-4697-89ac-f500b502883f-image-3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<h4>What Defines a Vintage-Inspired Ring?</h4><p>Vintage-inspired engagement rings take cues from historic jewellery design, often featuring details such as millgrain edging, filigree work, hand-engraved textures and distinctive diamond cuts. These thoughtful elements create depth, character and a sense of timelessness that feels both unique and enduring.</p>",
            "description_mobile": "<h4>What Defines a Vintage-Inspired Ring?</h4><p>Vintage-inspired engagement rings take cues from historic jewellery design, often featuring details such as millgrain edging, filigree work, hand-engraved textures and distinctive diamond cuts. These thoughtful elements create depth, character and a sense of timelessness that feels both unique and enduring.</p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
