          "settings": {
            "apply_overlay": false,
            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<h4>Consider the Details</h4><p>The beauty of vintage-inspired jewellery often lies in the finer details.</p><p>Our Bonnie Shield Ring features a trio of old mine cut diamonds set within a delicate millgrain frame, surrounded by intricate filigree-inspired detailing. Inspired by the elaborate artistry of the Rococo era, it offers a striking balance of romance and craftsmanship.</p><p>For those seeking a more understated approach, the Vintage Elongated Cushion Solitaire reimagines a classic silhouette through fluid lines and refined vintage details. Subtle textural elements enhance the ring's elegant form, creating a piece that feels timeless yet distinctly contemporary.</p>",
