            "devices": "mobile_desktop",
            "content_position": "underLeft",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "",
            "description": "<h4>Look to the Past for Inspiration</h4><p>Many of our vintage-inspired designs pay homage to historical design movements known for their beauty and ornamentation.</p><p>The Elaine Ring captures the femininity, grace and romance synonymous with the Rococo era. Fine millgrain detailing frames a tapered arrangement of old mine cut diamonds, resulting in a balanced and considered design suited to everyday wear or as a non-traditional engagement ring.</p><p>Similarly, our limited-edition Yesterday, Today collection celebrates the union of old and new. Featuring pre-loved gemstones, vintage design sensibilities and mindful workmanship, each piece is a tribute to enduring beauty and conscious craftsmanship. </p>",
            "description_mobile": "<h4>Look to the Past for Inspiration</h4><p>Many of our vintage-inspired designs pay homage to historical design movements known for their beauty and ornamentation.</p><p>The Elaine Ring captures the femininity, grace and romance synonymous with the Rococo era. Fine millgrain detailing frames a tapered arrangement of old mine cut diamonds, resulting in a balanced and considered design suited to everyday wear or as a non-traditional engagement ring.</p><p>Similarly, our limited-edition Yesterday, Today collection celebrates the union of old and new. Featuring pre-loved gemstones, vintage design sensibilities and mindful workmanship, each piece is a tribute to enduring beauty and conscious craftsmanship. </p>",
            "colour_style": "dark",
