            "description": "<h4>Finding a Ring That Feels Like You</h4><p>While vintage-inspired rings reference the past, the right piece should still feel personal to you.</p><p>The Lia Solitaire Ring embodies this balance beautifully. Designed to honour life's most meaningful moments, it pairs a timeless oval-cut diamond with a flattering split band and delicate vintage wirework. The result is a classic solitaire with a subtle vintage twist. Perfect for those seeking elegance with character.</p><p></p><h4>Choosing Your Future Heirloom</h4><p>A vintage-inspired engagement ring is more than a reflection of style; it is a celebration of craftsmanship, sentiment and enduring design. Whether you're drawn to intricate detailing, historic influences or the romance of a future heirloom, the perfect ring is one that tells your story while carrying the beauty of the past into the future.</p>",
